#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thig3.7:3.1"
msgid "7. Selātherīgāthā"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc57"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts57"></a>
msgctxt "thig3.7:4.1"
msgid "“Natthi nissaraṇaṃ loke,"
msgstr "There isn't any escape in the world"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.7:4.2"
msgid "kiṃ vivekena kāhasi;"
msgstr "What will seclusion do for you?"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.7:4.3"
msgid "Bhuñjāhi kāmaratiyo,"
msgstr "Enjoy the delights of sensual pleasure"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.7:4.4"
msgid "māhu pacchānutāpinī”."
msgstr "Don't regret it later"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc58"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts58"></a>
msgctxt "thig3.7:5.1"
msgid "“Sattisūlūpamā kāmā,"
msgstr "Sensual pleasures are like swords and stakes"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.7:5.2"
msgid "khandhāsaṃ adhikuṭṭanā;"
msgstr "The aggregates are an executioner’s block"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.7:5.3"
msgid "Yaṃ tvaṃ ‘kāmaratiṃ’ brūsi,"
msgstr "What you call 'delight in sensual pleasure'"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.7:5.4"
msgid "‘aratī’ dāni sā mama."
msgstr "Is now non-delight for me"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc59"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts59"></a>
msgctxt "thig3.7:6.1"
msgid "Sabbattha vihatā <span class=\"var\" title=\"nandi (bj, s2, s3, pts1-2)\" id=\"note27\">nandī</span>,"
msgstr "This delight is defeated everywhere"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.7:6.2"
msgid "Tamokhandho padālito;"
msgstr "I’ve put an end to the mass of darkness"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.7:6.3"
msgid "Evaṃ jānāhi pāpima,"
msgstr "So know this evil one:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.7:6.4"
msgid "Nihato tvamasi antakā”ti."
msgstr "You're defeated, ended"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta"><a class="sc" id="4"></a>
msgctxt "thig3.7:7.1"
msgid "…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "thig3.7:7.2"
msgid "Selā therī …."
msgstr ""
